    <h1 style="color:black" align="center">TERM AND CONDITIONS</h1>
	<p style="background-color:white">The RENT-A-LOVER website is a web developed by Kago Kevin Malokwane Sianang, inspierd by the shown anime "RentA-Girlfriend" and Japanese pop culture
	as a way to help people find comfort in new love and help people connect and socialize during their hardest moments.Having a girlfriend entails shouting, quarreling, and nagging, as well as shelling out cash on pricey dinners
	and excursions and giving up some of your solitude. When you rent a girlfriend, 
	you do away with all of these drawbacks and replace them with simply the advantages of having a partner—with the exception of any sexual
	components because it's against the law to trade sexual favors for cash or commodities. </p>
	 
