<p style="background-color: white"> Will I Get the “Lover Experience?”.</p>
<p style="background-color:white">Be extremely explicit with me. Only platonic friendships are permitted with the Friends that are offered 
for hire on RentAFriend. All of the girlfriends available for hire on RentAFriend.com are platonic. They don't provide any tangible services.
 No sexual activity, touching, kissing, etc. Everything that happens has to be platonic in nature..</p>
<p style="background-color:white">How Much Does it Cost to Rent a Lover?</p>
<p style="background-color:white">The girlfriends offered for rent on RentALover.com start at just $10 per hour, but depending on the occasion, activity, etc., many are adjustable or ready to forgo their price. For instance, you will probably have to cover the friend's costs if you want them to join you at a business event,
 a wedding, a party, etc. However, many of the buddies may think twice about lowering,
 if not completely waiving, their cost if you have tickets to the hottest concert, athletic event, or other special event.</p>
